These are Wayang Golek Purwa (Purwa Wooden Puppet). The story's mainly associated with Sundanese culture of West Java. Wayang Golek was once used to proselytize Muslim values, until it moved to Priangan West Java in the 18th century and used to tell romantic stories from the classic Indian epics; the Mahabharata and the Ramayana.
